  "subject": "Remove unused branches in UUI",
  "commit_message": "Remove unused branches in UUI\n\nThe jobs especially the docker build jobs running on Istanbul branch\nwill override the UUI docker images with tag latest.\n\nUUI doesn't need running on Istanbul branch anymore, so remove it.\nAnd there is no Kohn branch yet, also remove it.\n\nSigned-off-by: xudan16 <xudan16@huawei.com>\nIssue-ID: CIMAN-420\nChange-Id: Iec5dbc6fc357e84faf892075e17964b481ce67b8\n",
